E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I'm sorry if you don't like it, man, but I ain't in the gambling business.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~你不能接受的话，抱歉了。但我是不会冒这个险的。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~~c~ What am I going to do? What am I going to do?
~z~Maybe a third or forth home, but home nonetheless. It will be sad to say goodbye.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~可能是第三或第四个家，但总归是家。要走了，我好伤心。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~It'll be way down, brethren. Later on.
~z~You don't wanna follow your buddy, or do you?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~你是不是想跟那哥们一起下去？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~My life is fucked now. Without the Amir family, I've got nothing left.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我这辈子都完了，没有Amir家族支持，我什么都没有。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~- Look at the real estate. Enjoy. ~n~ - Where the fuck is Yusuf?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~－看看这些地产，爽吧。 ~n~－Yusuf他妈人呢？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~And now, I have to meet Ahmed and his brother to take a business meeting.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~现在又要去跟Ahmed和他兄弟谈生意。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~But if you don't get that it's a bit like,
~z~We were hoping to get Yusuf on wiretap. They don't know shit about you. Believe me!
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我们只想给Yusuf装窃听器。他们不知道你是谁，相信我！

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Oh! Thank goodness. If it's not Poppa, I can't think why you are so agitated.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~噢！谢天谢地。老爸都不在，那你慌什么慌。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Thanks, bro. Let's hope I don't have to use it.
~z~I'm a workaholic man. A workaholic, homie.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我可是工作狂啊。纯种的工作狂，哥们。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, you're gonna have to do your forgetting by yourself, man. I got a lot of other business to deal with. I'll see you round, man. Okay?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~你自己一个人去忘记过去吧，我还要忙呢。再见了哥们。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Tahir did. And Ahmed soon after him.
~z~Tahir is dead already. Please. Let me go.
~z~Yeah, at least we ain't in the jailhouse. I'll see you later, bro.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~唉，没进局子就行。再见了，兄弟。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~You better tell me where the fuck we at, bro!
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~你最好把来龙去脉交代清楚，兄弟！

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~You sound like a cop! I hope they weren't being legit with me, bro. I'll talk to you soon, you maniac.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~你又不是条子！希望他们是真的居心不轨。以后再聊，你个疯子。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Yo Ahmed, what these NOOSE assholes know?
~z~What you so het up about? Poppa ain't in town, is he?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~有什么好慌的？我爸不在城里吧？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~- he shall sweat in the desert to make amends, oh, for about 30 years. I'm sorry to have put you through this.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~在沙漠里做牛做马赎罪，搞上三十年。很抱歉把你牵连进来了。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~- Roll with me. You have to roll, but not like a fat man rolling, but just walk. ~n~ -Can we just go?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~－迈开腿。说是这么说，但不是劝肥仔迈开腿，就是要走起来。~n~－下去再说吧？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~If I was you, I'd leave the country.
~z~Dude took a dive down to sea level, bro.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~这哥俩来了个高空跳台，兄弟。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Here's hoping I don't need to use this shit.
~z~Get away from me, you crazy motherfucker.
~z~Sorry, man. I lost track of you. Can we do this another time?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~抱歉哥们，我走丢了。能不能改天再约？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Fucking snake better get outta town or there'll be trouble.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~阴险小人，快滚吧，不然有你好果子吃。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Tell me what I just walked into.
~z~Cruise on up to Rotterdam Tower. We gots a meet, man.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~向鹿特丹塔前进，我们要开个会，哥们。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Fuck. What do they know. Is it about the Buzzard?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我操。他们知道多少？是秃鹰的事吗？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~but he's obsessed with what they won't sell him.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~但他更中意自己买不到的东西。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I got greedy. I shouldn't have tried to set you up.
~z~Thank you, brother. Call me when you know it's alright, alright? Cheerio 'til then.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~谢了，兄弟。可以了就打电话给我，好吗？再见。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~You tell him I don't care. A billion dollars is chump change.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~告诉他我不在乎。十亿美元算个屁啊。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Tell me what the fuck is going on?
~z~Really? Shit. This city has become like home to me.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~真的吗？我操，自由城现在是我家啊。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Calm down, will you? I'll see you in a moment.
~z~No taste! I mean, I love those guys, but seriously, come on...
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~没有品味！我是喜欢他们，但说真的，天啊...

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Make out that we've got shit going down. Going down, my nigga!
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~确保事情能够办成。办成事，黑鬼！

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I wanted to take over his business. It was the wrong thing to do.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我想要抢走他的生意，是我错了。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Ahmed. Ahmed. I know that man too well. Something is afoot.
~z~I-I-I told you to chill, man. Shit.
~z~Head over to Rotterdam Tower, me bredren.
~z~Motherfuckers set you up with the NOOSE so they could take your business.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~他们联合国安办算计你，想要瓜分你的生意。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Act like we're friends. Shit, we are friends, baby!
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~就像朋友一样。我操，我们就是朋友，宝贝！

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I thank you for sparing him, my friend. It could not have been easy. Ah, I shall have to have him sent back to the Gulf -
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~太谢谢你放过他了，好朋友。真不容易啊。啊，真该送他回海湾地区。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I appreciate this, Luis. Hit me up when you're sure shit with them boys is cool. So long.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~太感谢了，Luis。完事了就打电话给我吧。再见。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, shit, I'm coming, man. Chill the f out.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~对，妈的，我过来了，哥们。你他妈别急。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~That don't sound good to me neither, bro. Keep your head down.
~z~Having this gun out wouldn't look too friendly.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~把枪掏出来是不是不太友好。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~If I see another tourist today, I'll puke.
~z~You know what they are, Luis? I'll level with you, they're very, what's the word? Tacky!
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~知道我怎么评价吗，Luis？我只跟你说，他们都很...那啥来着？俗气！

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I let him slide, bro. He ain't got no proof against us.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我放他「溜」了。他没有对我们不利的证据。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I should put my gun away. That shit might not set the right tone.
~z~You said he said he'd be here.
~z~These guys, they're always going on about how rich they are, "look the money here, the money there".
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~这些人一天到晚出去炫富，「看啊看啊，老子真有钱」。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~When I say bounce, I don't mean bouncing literally, I just mean...
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我说的「弹射」，不是字面上的那个弹射，我是说...

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Only time I like getting deep in shit is when I'm rear-ending models, man. This doesn't sound good.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我只有在操逼的时候才玩得大。听上去不太妙啊。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~No, you tell him that. You tell him Yusuf Amir is speaking. That name does mean something in this town!
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~不，你跟他说。告诉他，我是Yusuf Amir。老子是城里响当当的人物！

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Please, I'm like a brother to Yusuf. He wouldn't want me dead.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~求你了，Yusuf把我当兄弟，他不想让我死。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~If these guys is jumpy, they ain't gonna want to see this gun.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~那帮人提心吊胆的，可不想看到枪吧。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Yusuf's in town, baby. And your shit 'bout to be inadequate.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~Yusuf来了，宝贝。你们的楼压根不够看的。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~He thinks my life is one long party - a reckless orgy of sex, drugs and spending.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~他觉得我在花天酒地，生活中只有女人、毒品和花钱。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~What does a billion dollars buy anyway today? It doesn't even buy a million dollars.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~这年头的十亿还有什么用？压根就不值十亿了都。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~We gonna buy that piece-of-shit dirt-hole Middle Park, and turn it into a champagne swimming pool!
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我们把那个垃圾堆一样的中心公园买下来，改造成香槟泳池！

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~It ain't good, bro. We in some real deep shit.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~不太妙，兄弟。这下我们玩大了。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~No, no, no, no. Hey, you're coming with me, baby. You need to hang around.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~别别别别别别。嘿，你跟我一起去，宝贝，一起出去转转。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Yes, Poppa, yes, a present. It's a gift. No. No, you didn't pay for it. I did. Well, I didn't pay for it, so you didn't...
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~对，爸，对的，有份礼物，有份礼物。不不不，不用你掏钱，我都掏了。其实没花钱，也没用你的钱...

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~You got a long way to fall.
~z~Man this town is full of degenerates.
~z~Luis, what happened? I saw choppers on the Tower.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~Luis怎么了？我看到塔上来了直升机。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~What you mean, "what's going on?" Chill, homeboy.
~z~Fuck it. I deserve to die. Do what you will.
~z~Don't worry, we'll buy a new one.
~z~One second. Hello? Excuse me. Hello? Hello, who is this? Poppa! How are you?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~等下，喂？听得见吗？喂？喂，你哪位？爸爸！老爸你好吗？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~It may be nothing, but I've got a sixth sense for this shit.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~也可能没事，但直觉告诉我事出反常。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Yo, what the fuck's going on, man?
~z~Okay, bro. I'll head on up there for you.
~z~I dunno, man. Ahmed had an accident before I could get the info outta him, so we in the dark.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~不知道，哥们。我还没问出来，Ahmed就死了。多的我也不懂了。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I work my fingers to the bone. To the bone! You know, last week I got exhausted test driving sexy cars.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~为工作我可是拼了命的，拼了命的！上星期，我在累死累活地试驾豪车。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I am giving you this special auto shotgun with exploding shells.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~给你一把特别的全自动霰弹枪，能打炸药的。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Well, ten million dollars is maybe a little bit too much to spend in a month, but it was necessary.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~呃，一千万一个月确实有点多，但真的很有必要。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~He's a very conservative man. He does not understand what I'm doing here.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~他这人太保守了，根本不明白我在干什么。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~If this don't come in handy now, it might later. Thanks, bro.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~现在用不上，以后也会用上的。谢了，兄弟。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Look, here, I have a parachute. Take it.
~z~Okay, well, I guess I'll see you later, then.
~z~Tell those bitches at Rotterdam theirs ain't gonna be the tallest tower for long.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~跟Rotterdam那边管事的说，自由城第一高就要换一栋楼了。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I had to fly to Vice City and bang bitches for two weeks just to recover.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~坐飞机去罪城，操了两个星期的逼才恢复过来。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Poppa, it's complicated. I miss you, Poppa. I do. Yes, I'm close to closing the deal. The biggest tower. You're going to be so proud of me.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~老爸，别纠结了。我想你了，爸。真的。对，生意就快成了。通天巨塔。你会为我骄傲的。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~He's acting like a bitch and I can't figure out why.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~他样子不对劲，我也不知道原因。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~We just wanted Yusuf out of the picture.
~z~I cannot believe it. They were brothers to me. I would have brought them anything they wanted.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~真是不敢相信，他们是我的兄弟啊。想要啥我都能满足的。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Excuse me a moment, please. I have to call Ahmed. Make sure it's all cool and safe and that.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~不好意思，我给Ahmed打个电话，确保那边没出岔子。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Do you mind going up to the observation deck and conversating with them?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~你可以去观景台跟他们聊聊吗？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Ahmed, what's up, man? Why the stress? You sound perturbed!
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~Ahmed，怎么了，哥们？慌什么？声音有点抖啊！

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Do you mind going up to the observation deck and checking it out?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~你不介意去观景台看下情况吧？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Snitching motherfucker. I didn't do nothing to you.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~告密的贱逼，我跟你无冤无仇。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Stay away from me. Stay away from me.
~z~I'll just hit Ahmed up on my burner, man. Make sure shit is going down.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我用匿名号码联系下Ahmed，确保不会被放鸽子。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~What's up, papa? Trouble with your old man?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~怎么了，老兄？跟大爷闹别扭了？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I have a special gift, Luis. An auto shotgun with explosive shells!
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~给你一份特别的礼物，Luis。打炸药的，全自动霰弹枪！

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~You're looking at a city about to belong to us, motherfucker.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~你眼前的这座城市马上就是我们的了，妈个逼的。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Okay, man, if you say you're cool, you're cool. We'll be there in a moment.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，哥们，你说没事那就没事吧。我马上到。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Arab nigga! Wassup? What you looking at, bitch?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~阿拉伯黑鬼！你好吗？现在在看啥呢，贱人？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I don't have a good feeling about this. Ahmed is not himself. Very fucking weird.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~感觉不太对劲。Ahmed像变了个人，太古怪了。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Hey, it's you my friend, how you doing? How you doing?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，是你啊，朋友，还好吗？还好吗？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Shit. They were brothers to me! You didn't even give them a chance to explain?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，那都是我的好兄弟啊！你连个解释的机会都不给吗？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~This was meant to be a simple set up.
~z~Yeah, man. I'm okay. Your buddy, Tahir - not so much.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~对，哥们，我没事。你兄弟Tahir就不好说了。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~They wanted the NOOSE to take you down so they could control your operations.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~只要国安办干掉你，你的生意就归他们了。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~No, Poppa, no, that's not fair. No, no, no. Poppa, they're not prostitutes! They're loose women!
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~不，爸爸，不，这不公平。不不不。爸爸，那都不是妓女！破鞋而已！
~z~是，兄弟。国安办来了，冲我们来的。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Guy hit the pavement somewhere near terminal velocity.
~z~I have a deep sadness in me, Luis. Will you join me, please - for an orgy of champagne,
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~太让我伤心了，Luis。求你了，能不能跟我喝个烂醉、

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~You best get your chopper outta here.
~z~You'll feel like you're floating on air.
~z~No one will fuck with you. I'm giving you this special auto shotgun with explosive shells!
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~这下没人敢搞你了。给你把特别的全自动霰弹枪，打炸药的！

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I didn't wanna chance nothing, bro. I came at 'em with some heat straight off.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我不想冒风险，兄弟，上去就把他们突突了。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I haven't heard this voice since they shot that poor polo pony of yours at school.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~上次这么说话，还是你的马球马在学校被人打死的时候。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Luis, bro, I heard the news. What went down?
~z~Let's hope I don't need to use 'em.
~z~He knows, he fucking knows. We're in the shit.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~他懂了，他他妈都知道了，我们完了。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~cocaine, women, watermelons and whatever else this city may have to offer.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~嗑药、操逼、吃西瓜，反正城里能玩到的都可以。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~Really? Ah, this is terrible. Are you alright?
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~真的吗？啊，太可怕了。你没事吧？

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~You were right, bro. Those guys set you up, man.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~你说对了，兄弟。他们想算计你。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~I mean, I love those guys; they're like family, but, oh God, it's going to exhaust me.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~我真的喜欢他们，把他们当家人，但是，天，这也太累人了。

E2Y2AUD.original: ~z~It's a term from the street meaning you have to walk.
E2Y2AUD.translated: ~z~街溜子都是这么说的，意思是该走了。
